  "detailed_description": "<br><br>Hey There, Hotel Heroes! 🌟<br>Jump into the exciting world of \"Hotel Business Simulator,\" where you're the brains behind the ultimate hotel empire. Transform a humble spot into the talk of the town, turning a basic bed and breakfast into a luxurious resort. Your choices, your empire!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738870/extras/6dab573cc60750989221786373a77fb7.poster.avif?t=1734946617\" width=618 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738870/extras/6dab573cc60750989221786373a77fb7.webm?t=1734946617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738870/extras/6dab573cc60750989221786373a77fb7.mp4?t=1734946617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>What's Inside Your Hotel Empire:<br>- Stars in Your Eyes: Your hotel's success is all about its stars. Upgrade and embellish to go from a modest establishment to a high-end luxury resort.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738870/extras/5023d5698004326ef329b336274e0097.poster.avif?t=1734946617\" width=618 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738870/extras/5023d5698004326ef329b336274e0097.webm?t=1734946617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738870/extras/5023d5698004326ef329b336274e0097.mp4?t=1734946617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>- Rooms with Personality: Every room is a blank canvas. Will it be minimalist chic or opulent splendor? The more upscale the room, the more upscale the clientele.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738870/extras/3a576aaeb4db7a9cb38aabe20d9650b5.poster.avif?t=1734946617\" width=618 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738870/extras/3a576aaeb4db7a9cb38aabe20d9650b5.webm?t=1734946617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738870/extras/3a576aaeb4db7a9cb38aabe20d9650b5.mp4?t=1734946617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>- Guests' Delight: Keep those guests grinning from check-in to check-out. Cater to their needs, from the basic to the extravagant, and watch your popularity rise.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738870/extras/c7edd3378a55441e2fa6bef399d4018b.poster.avif?t=1734946617\" width=618 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738870/extras/c7edd3378a55441e2fa6bef399d4018b.webm?t=1734946617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738870/extras/c7edd3378a55441e2fa6bef399d4018b.mp4?t=1734946617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>- Cash Flow Management: Set your room rates wisely. Balance splendor with cost-effectiveness to maximize those profits.<br>- Spotless Reputation: Cleanliness is next to godliness in the hotel biz. A clean room is essential for guest satisfaction.<br>- Understanding Your Guests: Each guest comes with their own set of expectations. Match them with the perfect room to ensure their stay is memorable.<br>- Day's End: When the sun sets, it’s time for a well-deserved rest. Prepare for the next day of bustling hotel management!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738870/extras/38ef47681b6e7817e1ae84bda7ca7529.poster.avif?t=1734946617\" width=618 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738870/extras/38ef47681b6e7817e1ae84bda7ca7529.webm?t=1734946617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738870/extras/38ef47681b6e7817e1ae84bda7ca7529.mp4?t=1734946617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>\"Hotel Business Simulator\" is more than a game; it’s your journey to becoming a hospitality mogul. Are you ready to create, decorate, and run the hotel of your dreams? Let the business begin!",
